        <item>
            <title>传 Nothing 将推头戴式耳机，支援消噪功能 + 全透明 LED 灯带设计</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/nothing-rumors-head1-in-development/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nothing-rumors-head1-in-development</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/10/nothing-rumors-head1-in-development/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Edward]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 10 Feb 2025 03:00:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技新闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Head (1)]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Nothing]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1290672</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>提起 Nothing 这个品牌，早前就已传出多项有关他们最新智能手机的消息，但今次的消息就有点不同，根据消息指出，Nothing 似乎有意在今年推出旗下首款头戴式耳机 Head (1)。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290675" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_003.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290674" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002-694x462.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="462" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002-694x462.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_002.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1290676" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/nothingearphone_004.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>其实 Nothing 推出耳机也不是甚么新鲜事，在他们旗下现时已有多款真无线蓝牙耳机，包括：Ear、Ear (a)、CMF Buds、Ear Stick、Ear (open) 等，不过如果真的推出 Head (1)，就真的是旗下首款头戴式耳机款式。据消息指，这款开发代号名为 B170 的耳机，将会具备十分不错的消噪功能，而且支援 5W 充电格式，而早在大约年半前，Nothing 的 CEO 裴宇就已在 X 分享过由支持者设计的 Head (1) 渲染图，所以今日流出他们有意推出旗下首款头戴式耳机，绝非空穴来风。不过有关这款耳机就暂时未有进一步消息，是否真的采用与手机及其他耳机相同的透明式 + LED 灯带设计，以及各项规格依然是个谜。希望今年稍后时份我们可以获得更多进一步消息，之后再为各位 unwire.hk 读者揭晓吧。</p><p>来源：<a href="https://www.smartprix.com/bytes/nothing-might-launch-wireless-headphones-later-this-year/">smartprix</a>、<a href="https://x.com/getpeid/status/1580001210450731008">X</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
